To announce in JavaScript (typical)

// create the event first
event = new Event()
   .name( 'event.name.here' )
   .display_context( 'jquery addressable selector' )
   .display_mode( 'append|replace|prepend|etc' )
   .attr( 'name', 'value' )
   .values();

